<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>New Replay Notification</title>
    <style type="text/css">
      body {
        font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        color: #000; /* Set font color to black */
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        height: 100vh;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #4f5ef1; /* Set border color */
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        color: #000; /* Set font color to black */
      }
      .message-sm { /* Apply the same styles to .footer as .message-sm */
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        padding-top: 50px;
        padding-bottom: 50px; 
        background-color: #3498db; 
        color: #fff; 
      }
      .course-info {
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      table, td {
        border: 1px solid #0000002f;
        color: #000; /* Set font color to black */
      }
      .first-td {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 8px;
      }
      .second-td {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 8px;
      }
      .table-row {
        border-top: 1px solid #00000029;
      }
      .col-2 {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 8px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .footer p {
        margin: 5px 0;
      }
      .footer { 
        margin-top: 5%;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        padding-top: 50px;
        padding-bottom: 50px; 
        background-color: #34d0db; 
        color: #fff; 
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="message-sm">
        <h1>Your E-Learning order is confirmed...!</h1>
        <p>And we're just as excited as you are.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="course-info">
        <h4>Here's what you have ordered:</h4>
        <table style="border-bottom: 1px solid #0000002f">
          <tr>
            <td>Order #: <%= order._id %></td>
            <td>Order Date: <%= order.date %></td>
          </tr>
        </table>
        <table style="width: 90%; margin: auto;">
          <tr>
            <td class="first-td">Item</td>
            <td class="first-td">Quantity</td>
            <td class="first-td">Cost</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="second-td"><%= order.name %></td>
            <td class="second-td">1</td>
            <td class="second-td"><%= order.price %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="col-2">Subtotal:</td>
            <td class="col-2"><%= order.price %></td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          If you have any questions, please contact our support team at
          <a href="mailto:adarshaadi1997@gmail.com">adarshaadi1997@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
        <p>&copy; 2023 E-Learning. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
